    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>LEAD: Although Christmas is over, the celebration continues at the Van Cortlandt Manor in Croton-on-Hudson, N.Y. An ''Old Christmas,'' with music, food and candlelight tours, will be held through Sunday at the restoration. Hours each day are 5 to 9 P.M. Admission is $4 ($3.50 for the elderly; $2.50 for those 6 to 14).</p>
      </block>
